videos.headline: Ref gets trucked on Virginia's 62-yard INT return
videos.description: Virginia's Juan Thornhill runs over a referee on a 62-yard interception return, setting up the Cavaliers in the red zone.

videos.headline: Virginia goes up the middle for a 7-yard score
videos.description: Jordan Ellis runs up the middle for a 7-yard touchdown to give Virginia a 10-0 lead on Miami.

videos.headline: Ref gets trucked on Virginia's 62-yard INT return
videos.description: Virginia's Juan Thornhill runs over a referee on a 62-yard interception return, setting up the Cavaliers in the red zone.

videos.headline: Canes' Rosier keeps it himself for 11-yard score
videos.description: Malik Rosier's 11-yard touchdown cuts Miami's deficit to 16-13.

videos.headline: Virginia fans rush the field
videos.description: Virginia fans rush the field after upsetting Miami 16-13.
